019-11-01T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"【白宮聯署 】依個就快截止⚠️<br />\n1. 制裁TVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32jy4fj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32jy4fj&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=7a88a8d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32jy4fj</a><br />\n尚欠60000人聯署，11月9日截止。<br />\n2. 解散警隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31gWPHR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31gWPHR&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=5ce5d931\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31gWPHR</a><br />\n尚欠 16000 人聯署，11 月 9日截止。<br />\n簽&gt;記得email確認&gt;傳開去"},{"pid":"4b5143da48397edc69ac730e8b5af5513ec1a2fe","tid":1686871,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a1bbec68d6c3790abc95a3271e18f1f71edc63b","tid":1686871,"uid":278392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"支那game 睇都唔想睇<br />\nBtw不推文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GHOSTPIEgames/posts/416477475695819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGHOSTPIEgames%2Fposts%2F416477475695819&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=2e7c475e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GHOSTPIEgames/posts/416477475695819</a><br />\n<br />\nHello 大家好！ 我們是Ghostpie，感謝各位的長期關注。<br />\n<br />\n《牛一》 正式更名為《港詭實錄》，<br />\n將會登陸Steam 與PS4 平臺；<br />\n《牛一》 將會在遊戲發售後以DLC的形式推出。<br />\n<br />\n《港詭實錄》的Steam商店頁面已經開放，如果大家對遊戲有興趣的話，不妨到以下鏈接 加入心願清單。<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1178490/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1178490%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=01a3251c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1178490/</a><br />\n<br />\n《港詭實錄》&shy;是一款以現代香港為背景的恐怖冒險遊戲，融合了香港本地的都市傳說與真實案件。<br />\n玩家能夠從中體驗到許多獨特的香港本地文化和民俗習慣。同時，在遊戲中我們還原了唐樓、粵劇戲棚、公共屋邨等極具香港特色的建築，讓各位自由探索的同時，感受濃厚的香港氣息。<br />\n通過這款遊戲，我們想讓更多人可以去了解民俗，<br />\n了解傳統文化，了解香港。<br />\n<br />\n在此為大家獻上《港詭實錄》的首發預告，<br />\n發售日期與詳情將會在不久公佈。<br />\n<br />\n由於遊戲進入了緊張的後期打磨階段，<br />\n可能沒有辦法及時回覆各位的留言。<br />\n還望大家諒解。<br />\n謝謝各位的支持和鼓勵！<br />\n<br />\nHello, we are Ghostpie.<br />\nParanormal HK will be coming soon on PS4 and Steam.<br />\nPlease add to your wishlist on Steam page：<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1178490/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1178490%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=01a3251c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1178490/</a><br />\nParanormal HK is a first person horror adventure game about modern Hong Kong urban legends and criminal cases.<br />\n<br />\nLaunch date and details will be anounced soon, thanks for your support!<br />\n<br />\n#香港遊戲 #indie game #<span style=\"color: red;\">本土</span> #Horror #PS4 #PC #牛一 #港詭實錄<br />\n<br />\n本土WO"},{"pid":"433e3beb6d8112c96143b0573f5783918294af11","tid":1686871,"uid":100016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"淨係句中國香港已經夠噁心啦，得閒幫隻game染黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beab8d796a72a9922dbbb6d01fee25caf6e7435a","tid":1686871,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4b5143da48397edc69ac730e8b5af5513ec1a2fe","tid":1686871,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a1bbec68d6c3790abc95a3271e18f1f71edc63b","tid":1686871,"uid":278392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"支那game 睇都唔想睇<br />\nBtw不推文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GHOSTPIEgames/posts/416477475695819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGHOSTPIEgames%2Fposts%2F416477475695819&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=2e7c475e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">